        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/reg67/{size}/54198_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-10-20T19:19:23.608Z",
        "cooked": "<p>There’s currently 2 separate toggles on the phone number privacy pane: who can see my number and who can find me by number.</p>\n<p>However, there are essentially only 3 options:<br>\nEveryone can see and find by phone number<br>\nNo one can see phone number, but everyone can find by phone number<br>\nNo one can see or find by phone number</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/9/6/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/6/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72_2_312x375.jpeg\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"lpFrpBusMI6cCnQYKujajIicQaS\" width=\"312\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/6/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72_2_312x375.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/6/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72_2_468x562.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/9/6/9614741d579d86797fdfe65f754c043f64756d72_2_624x750.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EFEFF0\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1170×1404 101 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>The design has a lot of room for improvement. It presents 4 options for the user to choose while there are really only 3 selectable options. A 3-step slider would be best for this pane, for example:<br>\nNo one - Find only - Everyone</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
